{"tid":582384,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"香港任天堂nintento eshop 4月3號正式上線了","createTime":"2018-03-06T06:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T14:35:00.000Z","uid":119778,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d919f7097addc6db6de06a547de83cf5c13fc508","tid":582384,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T06:26:25.000Z","msg":"4月3日（預定）<br />\n<br />\n● 關於Nintendo eShop<br />\n香港Nintendo eShop可以透過兌換在任天堂(香港)指定的網上商店購買的各種下載版遊戲軟體及新增內容的下載序號，從而使用各種遊戲軟體及新增內容。<br />\n<br />\n＊可以在香港Nintendo eShop上進行的事<br />\n・ 使用下載序號來兌換各種遊戲軟體及新增內容<br />\n・ 重新下載兌換遊戲軟體 <br />\n<br />\n＊不可以在香港Nintendo eShop上進行的事 <br />\n・ 瀏覽商品資訊及使用餘額支付各種新增內容<br />\n・ 對戰及協力等透過網路進行的網路遊戲<br />\n※透過網路通訊進行的網路遊戲，以及使用整體Nintendo eShop的日期現階段為未定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85cbbdaf77cd640483c3802bfc7fa6808b3585e","tid":582384,"uid":124107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T06:33:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1d4f33c017a941d1f0ad1f1c801c90b14417ca1","tid":582384,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b85cbbdaf77cd640483c3802bfc7fa6808b3585e","tid":582384,"uid":124107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T06:33:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:15:06.000Z","msg":"有 遲d"},{"pid":"1efdf2841746e390c96a4608c66c56f554f223fc","tid":582384,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"今次好垃圾<br />\n你點解唔直接屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7244f795ac8350f08821ea8f5c6352917736e5c","tid":582384,"uid":119778,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1efdf2841746e390c96a4608c66c56f554f223fc","tid":582384,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:15:48.000Z"